Meeting the MMC

Control panel > Administrative tools > Computer management > disk amangement

MMC - Microsoft Management Console

search MMC > add msc snapins > save 

list of msc

> diskmgmt.msc -  Disk Management
> perfmon.msc - Performance Monitor
> services.msc - Services
> lusrmgr.msc - Local Users and Groups
> secpol.msc - Local Security Policy
> gpedit.msc - Local Group Policy

Review 

	> Its sometimes too complex to find certain administrative tools
	> MMC makes it easier to use the toools you use the most
	> work smarter, not harder